  "title": "Quality Control Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title: Quality Control Technician </strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore (With free shuttle service from Choa Chu Kang & Joo Koon MRT stations)</p><ul><li><p>Perform precise quality checks using tools like calipers and gauges.</p></li><li><p>Support new production trials and monitor live processes to prevent issues.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with engineering and production teams to troubleshoot and improve workflows.</p></li><li><p>Maintain clear, accurate records and follow procedures to ensure compliance.</p></li><li><p>Help investigate root causes and contribute ideas for better, more efficient ways of working.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Comfortable with basic measurement tools and Microsoft Excel.</p></li><li><p>A true team player who thrives in a fast-paced, supportive environment.</p></li><li><p>Known for your keen eye for detail and a genuine desire to learn and grow.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Financial Reward & Security</strong></p><ul><li><p>Attractive pay: Basic salary of $2,500 – $2,600 + OT (total gross can reach $3,500+).</p></li><li><p>Daily support allowance of $10–$20 per shift.</p></li><li><p>13th-month bonus and variable performance bonus (up to 2 months).</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Choose a schedule: 5-day or 6-day work week.</p></li><li><p>11 days of annual leave to recharge.</p></li></ul><p><p>Clear career progression and professional development.</p></p><p>Easy commute with our free shuttle from Choa Chu Kang & Joo Koon MRT.<br /></p><p></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
